<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 09:13:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>尽管新能源汽车取得了里程碑式的进展，中国四月份汽车销量仍出现收缩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-april-car-sales-swing-contraction-despite-nev-milestone-2024-05-10/</link><description>周五的行业数据显示，中国 4 月份汽车销量同比下降 5.8%，原因是激烈的价格战和激励措施未能摆脱消费者在不稳定的经济复苏期间对大件商品支出的谨慎态度。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 08:45:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-april-car-sales-swing-contraction-despite-nev-milestone-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示坚决反对美国出口管制工具</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-says-it-firmly-opposes-us-export-control-tools-2024-05-10/</link><description>在美国出于国家安全考虑将37家中国企业列入贸易限制名单后，外交部发言人周五表示，中国坚决反对滥用美国实体清单等出口管制工具。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 08:24:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-says-it-firmly-opposes-us-export-control-tools-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>Porch 在美国起诉中国建设银行再保险欺诈损失</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/porch-sues-china-construction-bank-us-over-reinsurance-fraud-losses-2024-05-10/</link><description>美国保险和房屋检查软件提供商 Porch Group 正在起诉中国资产第三大银行中国建设银行 (CCB)，指控其实施“大规模欺诈”，给 Porch 造成“巨大损失”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 08:20:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/porch-sues-china-construction-bank-us-over-reinsurance-fraud-losses-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>第五招：走自己的路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/take-five/global-markets-themes-graphic-2024-05-10/</link><description>随着欧洲各地纷纷降息，全球央行开始摆脱困境，而美国的借贷成本可能会在更长时间内保持较高水平，从而提振美元。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 08:13:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/take-five/global-markets-themes-graphic-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>台湾发生5.8级地震，目前尚无受损报告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-rattled-by-58-magnitude-quake-no-immediate-reports-damage-2024-05-10/</link><description>台湾气象部门表示，周五，台湾东海岸发生了 5.8 级地震，目前尚未收到受损情况报告。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 07:53:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-rattled-by-58-magnitude-quake-no-immediate-reports-damage-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>韩国外相下周访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-foreign-minister-visit-china-next-week-2024-05-10/</link><description>首尔外交部周五表示，应中国外交部长王毅的邀请，韩国外交部长赵太烈将于下周一至周二访问中国。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 07:43:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-foreign-minister-visit-china-next-week-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国军方称其在南海“击退”了美国驱逐舰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-military-says-it-drove-away-us-destroyer-south-china-sea-2024-05-10/</link><description>中国人民解放军南部战区周五在一份声明中表示，中国军方表示，严密监视并“驱离”了5月10日进入南海西沙群岛领海的哈尔西号驱逐舰。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 07:29:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-military-says-it-drove-away-us-destroyer-south-china-sea-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰和平峰会推动中立瑞士拥抱西方</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-peace-summit-pushes-neutral-swiss-toward-western-embrace-2024-05-10/</link><description>即将举行的乌克兰和平峰会表面上是中立的瑞士多年来最雄心勃勃的调解重大冲突的努力，但实际上却表明瑞士的经济和安全利益如何在俄罗斯问题上日益与西欧保持一致。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 07:03:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-peace-summit-pushes-neutral-swiss-toward-western-embrace-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国风险投资家警告IPO冻结将打击创新</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-venture-capitalists-warn-ipo-freeze-will-hit-innovation-2024-05-10/</link><description>中国风险投资家警告称，中国的首次公开募股冻结导致市场参与者锁定现有投资，从而导致科技初创企业资金匮乏，从而破坏了北京当前推动经济创新的努力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 06:56:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-venture-capitalists-warn-ipo-freeze-will-hit-innovation-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>富士康第一季度利润从低基数跃升，人工智能推动增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/foxconns-q1-profit-jump-low-base-ai-power-growth-2024-05-10/</link><description>全球最大的合同电子产品制造商台湾富士康预计将于周二报告称，由于人工智能服务器的强劲需求以及去年同期的低基数，第一季度利润将增长一倍以上。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 06:44:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/foxconns-q1-profit-jump-low-base-ai-power-growth-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>南海争端升级 菲律宾呼吁驱逐中国外交官</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-calls-chinese-diplomats-be-expelled-disinformation-2024-05-10/</link><description>菲律宾国家安全顾问周五呼吁驱逐中国外交官，原因是涉嫌泄露与菲律宾海军上将的通话内容，导致南海争端大幅升级。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 05:15:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-calls-chinese-diplomats-be-expelled-disinformation-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>全球降息乐观情绪重燃，亚洲股市上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-10/</link><description>亚洲股市周五上涨，有望连续第三周上涨，而美元则保持稳定，因为美国劳动力市场宽松的新迹象在下周关键通胀数据公布之前引发了人们对今年降息的乐观情绪。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 02:31:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾希望提高镍加工能力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/philippines-says-us-china-eyeing-mining-opportunities-especially-nickel-2024-05-10/</link><description>菲律宾周五表示，在中国和美国等国表达对采矿业的兴趣后，菲律宾计划再增加三个加工厂，以发展其丰富的镍资源的下游产业。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 02:20:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/philippines-says-us-china-eyeing-mining-opportunities-especially-nickel-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国的绿色铝野心受到不稳定降雨和停电的打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-push-greener-aluminium-hit-by-erratic-rains-power-cuts-2024-05-10/</link><description>中国西南部地区降雨不稳定，导致耗资数十亿美元的铝工业绿色化进程受挫。该铝工业产量占全球产量近60%，据一些估计，其二氧化碳排放量比澳大利亚还多。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 02:09:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-push-greener-aluminium-hit-by-erratic-rains-power-cuts-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称拜登将对中国电动汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/us-set-impose-tariffs-china-evs-certain-strategic-sectors-bloomberg-reports-2024-05-10/</link><description>据两位知情人士透露，美国总统乔·拜登将于下周宣布对包括电动汽车在内的战略行业征收新的中国关税。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 01:05:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/us-set-impose-tariffs-china-evs-certain-strategic-sectors-bloomberg-reports-2024-05-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>